      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いや～、こんな風に遊ぶと……\nリズノワで沖縄に行った時のことを思い出しますね～",
      "startTime": 14.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8191383044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんや葵さんがナンパされたり\nスーツ姿の怪しい男性が物陰から見つめてきてたり……",
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それって俺のことか……？　でも懐かしいな\nあの時はなんだかんだで四人とも楽しんでたもんな",
      "startTime": 31.7323611677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.4544897397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "楽しかったですよ～！　莉央さんと葵さんの\nいつもとは違う一面も見れて……",
      "startTime": 39.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……こころ？",
      "startTime": 42.7739681561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.8572787801
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、スタッフさんが呼んでます",
      "startTime": 43.8572787801,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6203.4673681,
          "startTime": 50.0607461482
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、{user}さん、愛ちゃん！\n早く来ないと置いてっちゃいますよ～！",
      "startTime": 48.9002735504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7143534065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こころ……行ってしまった",
      "startTime": 51.7143534065,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5938.075701499997,
          "startTime": 57.652429108
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころのユニコーンちゃんにも、出番があるなんて～\nさあ、行きますよ～、愛ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 62.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ほ～らほ～ら、ゆらゆら～、ゆらゆら～\n愛ちゃん、振り落とされちゃダメですよ！",
      "startTime": 70.7309847139,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 375.69045610000273,
          "startTime": 65.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2942.3571227000025,
          "startTime": 67.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4242.357122699999,
          "startTime": 69.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "日頃から鍛えに鍛えた体幹を生かすチャンスです！\n次はもっと揺らしちゃいますね～",
      "startTime": 79.6999964396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こころは愛にイタズラするのが\n本当に好きだな……",
      "startTime": 84.7666600544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "おやおや？　こころにしがみついちゃって\nどうしたんですか？　可愛いですね～",
      "startTime": 89.4666656493,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 861.6309284000039,
          "startTime": 87.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、揺れのレベルMAXで……うぐっ。えっと……\n愛ちゃん？　そんなに強く抱きつかれると……",
      "startTime": 98.8333379108,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3520.0329400000073,
          "startTime": 96.9634641148
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3323.235491900007,
          "startTime": 96.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5066.662089200008,
          "startTime": 103.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8887.268316700001,
          "startTime": 107.7206062275
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8099.997456899999,
          "startTime": 106.9333353677
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5269.387805600005,
          "startTime": 104.1027257164
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13453.3307902,
          "startTime": 112.286668701
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 13453.3307902,
          "startTime": 112.286668701
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13456.936491700006,
          "startTime": 112.2902744025
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ふぎゅ～！？　愛ちゃん、ギブ、ギブ～！\n息が出来ない～……わっ、落ちる……ひゃ～～～！？",
      "startTime": 108.7000020343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、何をしてるんだか",
      "startTime": 113.9586045782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 118.465950024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "は～、今日ははしゃぎ過ぎました\nさすがにくたくたですよ～",
      "startTime": 123.56667277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。それにしても、愛はまっすぐ帰ったのに\nこころはどうして事務所まで来たんだ？",
      "startTime": 130.8000061033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　さっき言ったじゃないですか～\nちょっと忘れ物を取りに来ただけですよ",
      "startTime": 136.8000061033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "……なーんていうのは、まぁ……嘘なんですけどね",
      "startTime": 140.8200765568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのことで、何か相談したいことでもあるのか？",
      "startTime": 145.8846798697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "いきなり本題に入るのは野暮ですよ～、まったく\n……でも、そうですね、そんな感じです",
      "startTime": 155.2000061033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "最近……莉央さんも葵さんも凄く張り詰めてるんです\n「リズノワは今のままでいいのか」って",
      "startTime": 165.36667277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "だから……前に沖縄に行った時みたいに\nまた四人で遊べたらって思ったんです",
      "startTime": 172.1000061033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\n確かにCM撮影でも、いろいろあったみたいだしな",
      "startTime": 176.9333394366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今回のPR動画の撮影は\n莉央さんと葵さんが来られなくて……",
      "startTime": 184.3000061033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "それならせめて愛ちゃんとはっちゃけて、先輩方に\n「何してるんだか」って笑ってもらえたらなーって",
      "startTime": 191.16667277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……\nだから今日は、いつも以上にはしゃいでいたんだな",
      "startTime": 196.6333394366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
