      "text": "私はかっこいい莉央さんが、葵さんが、愛ちゃんが……\nかっこいいリズノワが好きなんです",
      "startTime": 234.9666676837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
